constraints_details.result: Hinterland Lower Lea Valley including Stratford

description: Retention and refurbishment of No. 25 Payne Road, the demolition of the remaining buildings, and the redevelopment of the site to provide new buildings up to 16 storeys high to provide 158 flats and 15 commercial units to accommodate Class B1, A1, A2 and D1 uses, with associated landscaping, car parking, and cycle storage.
